packing\ndata. The Appendix presents an overview of published monodisperse packing\nfractions of (sphero)cylinders for aspect ratios from zero to infinity, and at\nRLP and RCP packing configurations, and they are related to Onsager's theory.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Sep 2022 17:29:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 16 May 2023 09:46:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-17"}
