less, with no pillars present. However,\nthe densest portion of the cloud lies closest to the PDR, and the C$^{18}$O\nemission is flattened along the radiation front.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Sep 2022 21:43:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-30"}
