ely\nsigned and large in magnitude for the $\\alpha$-cristobalite phase. The elastic\nconstants, high-frequency dielectric constants, Born effective charge tensors,\nand thermal properties of the above phases of BeF$_2$ are reported for the\nfirst time and hence serve as predictions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Sep 2022 03:31:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-22"}
