t adds a useful tool for better\nunderstanding the propagation of deformations in the heel soft tissues that\ncould generate pressure ulcers. This methodology can be used to obtain data on\nthe material properties of the soft tissues to define constitutive laws for FE\nsimulations and finally it offers a promising technique for validating FE\nmodels.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Sep 2022 09:19:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-22"}
