id phases are obtained for\nseveral salt compositions of the system. Due to removal of restrictions\nresulting from a smaller number of components in ternary systems, the\nthermodynamic behavior of systems with a mixed composition of the salt is\nsignificantly differ from the behavior of those with a single salt component.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Sep 2022 13:39:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-22"}
